<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm und Nördlingen</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Markgraf Jobst von Mähren am Antoniustag in Brünn verstorben ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l3">. Vlm . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l4">Lieben frewnd / vvir laſʒen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> frewntſchaft vviſʒen / daʒ vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l5">botſchaft <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt / vvie das Margraf Jobs von Merhern / am Suntag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l7">nach ſant Anthonien tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l6"><expan>nehſtvergang<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> fünff hore auf den tag 
<del rend="strikethrough"> verſchie </del> cʒu Prünne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l8">verſchieden vnd von tods <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abgang<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeÿ / da vviſʒ ſich <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vveiſheit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l9">nach cʒu richten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Purificac<ex>i</ex>on<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>Mar<ex>ie</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l10"><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Sı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnd, wir laszen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan> frewntschaft wiszen, daz uns botschaft
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, wie das margraf Jobs von Merhern
                            <app><note><q type="date">am suntag nach sant Anthonien tag
                                    <add><expan>nehstvergang<ex>en</ex></expan></add></q>18.01.1411</note></app> fünff hore auf den
                        tag czu Prünne verschieden und von tods <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abgang<ex>en</ex></expan> sey, da wisz sich
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> weisheit nach czu richten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>purificac<ex>i</ex>on<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>Mar<ex>ie</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
